{"EpubVersion":2,"filepath":"","fixparentnode":"","floatingtheme":[],"folded":false,"markups":[{"date":"2025-03-24 22:09:12","docid":0,"id":2,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"辛丑年，农工商部派赵从番、魏梯云等人前往南洋慰问华侨，作者受友人魏梯云邀请同行。","page":5,"rect":[113.2499966248871,34.499998971819906,339.24998991936474,93.9999972283841],"type":11,"uuid":"c577d4c0e1f00df7a4cf2668c9f0f914"},{"date":"2025-03-24 22:13:04","docid":0,"id":3,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"公元1901年4月1日（公历）即为辛丑年二月十三日。当日早上10点，作者乘船路过西贡，但并未登岸。","page":14,"rect":[230.2499931380155,53.99999839067464,505.74998495727823,113.49999664723883],"type":11,"uuid":"fcb95cfb1bd61dc74cfc2c10080bc8b1"},{"CL":[179.99999463558214,207.7499938085677,251.6249925009908,105.4999974519015,251.6249925009908,85.4999974519015],"date":"2025-03-24 22:15:05","docid":0,"id":6,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"清政府向南洋华侨学校捐赠教科书及教育用品。","page":21,"rect":[158.2499952837826,49.499998524785084,345.999989718199,86.4999974519015],"type":9,"uuid":"1061e0b027c99a3e785ab31494b9cf50"},{"CL":[482.2499856278305,161.24999519437566,314.24999063462053,121.99999696016317,314.24999063462053,101.99999696016317],"date":"2025-03-24 22:18:04","docid":0,"id":9,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"在荷属殖民地，作者看到当地政府积极招揽学童进入学校，学习当地语言文字，而放弃中文。这让卓宏谋感到忧心忡忡，甚至有“以夷变夏”之虑。为了改变这一趋向，并且使得海外华侨倾心“内向”，卓主张重视海外华侨的中文教育。","page":26,"rect":[80.24999760836374,24.74999926239252,549.2499836608772,102.99999696016317],"type":9,"uuid":"714d1bdd042aa61ff6be877c821409d9"},{"CL":[193.4999942332508,127.49999620020401,291.3749913163486,109.24999734014281,291.3749913163486,89.24999734014281],"date":"2025-03-24 22:19:49","docid":0,"id":11,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"这里又有清政府向当地华侨学校赠送教科书的记载。","page":38,"rect":[191.24999430030607,45.74999863654379,392.4999883323911,90.24999734014281],"type":9,"uuid":"c3490ff738661e4be7483b3d6445af4b"},{"CL":[437.24998696893493,489.74998540431307,455.99998641014145,391.9999889135364,455.99998641014145,371.9999889135364],"date":"2025-03-24 22:20:31","docid":0,"id":13,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"清政府向当地赠送教科书。","page":39,"rect":[422.9999873936181,291.7499913051727,489.99998542666486,372.9999889135364],"type":9,"uuid":"c26be501f279aa9c5f4bb900988ccb34"},{"CL":[110.99999669194231,179.24999465793388,109.74999613314878,62.999998122453746,129.74999613314878,62.999998122453746],"date":"2025-03-24 22:21:23","docid":0,"id":15,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"赠送教科书。","page":42,"rect":[129.74999613314878,51.74999845772986,229.74999318271904,75.24999778717763],"type":9,"uuid":"1eac816946b849a4de6e9398e70471cc"},{"date":"2025-03-24 22:23:03","docid":0,"id":16,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"四月初八（公元1901年5月25日），开往西贡。","page":44,"rect":[232.49999307096027,48.749998547136826,564.9999831914906,82.74999756366022],"type":11,"uuid":"502865677824b307b7f1da4170e31aba"},{"CL":[96.7499971166254,208.49999378621598,114.37499659135948,89.74999792128807,114.37499659135948,69.74999792128807],"date":"2025-03-24 22:28:43","docid":0,"id":18,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"卓宏谋认为华商是“主人”。","page":44,"rect":[9.749999709427357,47.24999859184031,219.9999934732916,70.74999792128807],"type":9,"uuid":"71be07ad2768407122c2ed15a6e0a046"},{"date":"2025-03-24 22:29:09","docid":0,"id":19,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"《南洋群岛游记》一文使用“越南”一词。","page":45,"rect":[179.9999946355822,48.749998547136826,495.24998527020267,88.74999738484628],"type":11,"uuid":"2176f9047930d4f90b2654ed9f55d278"},{"CL":[282.7499915733936,476.9999857842926,279.74999166280054,702.9999784529216,279.74999166280054,722.9999784529216],"date":"2025-03-24 22:31:48","docid":0,"id":21,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"这恰恰说明西贡当地华侨存在着门户之见。","page":45,"rect":[194.2499942108991,722.9999784529216,366.24998911470203,769.7499770894653],"type":9,"uuid":"9f9ec6f75e51640d7d8eed4522fa110c"},{"CL":[476.24998580664436,332.99999007582693,459.9999856948857,364.1249891482297,479.9999856948857,364.1249891482297],"date":"2025-03-24 22:32:45","docid":0,"id":23,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"卓宏谋和友人游西贡动植物园。","page":46,"rect":[479.9999856948857,329.9999901652339,579.2499827668076,399.24998813122545],"type":9,"uuid":"ad5f0ee9fe2f516dd441ee4a54a66e89"},{"CL":[404.2499879524115,473.2499858960513,424.2499879524115,793.1249763630337,404.2499879524115,793.1249763630337],"date":"2025-03-24 22:33:50","docid":0,"id":25,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"卓宏谋乘坐军舰离开西贡，前往香港。","page":46,"rect":[257.99999231100105,768.7499770894653,405.2499879524115,818.4999756366021],"type":9,"uuid":"569db304549099a31a5932ea4c20fc07"},{"date":"2025-03-24 22:36:09","docid":0,"id":26,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"卓宏谋随清政府前往南洋慰问华侨，来、回均路过西贡，唯回程时登陆。该人在西贡活动较为简单，除了参加宴请之外，就是参观西贡动植物园、街头购物。《南洋群岛游记》一书对于西贡并无太多观察与思考。","page":46,"rect":[65.99999803304672,19.499999418854728,471.24998598545824,96.24999716132888],"type":11,"uuid":"87680add402f400dc947d212fd748962"},{"CL":[227.24999322742244,462.7499862089757,227.2499932274225,741.2499773129828,227.2499932274225,761.2499773129828],"date":"2025-03-24 22:37:36","docid":0,"id":28,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linewidth":12,"originaltext":"卓宏谋一行南下慰问侨胞搭乘的是“海琛”号军舰。","page":9,"rect":[125.24999626725923,761.2499773129828,330.24999018758575,800.4999761730439],"type":9,"uuid":"72145bc908072dd3af0e31a628e32f7f"}],"maxid":28,"notelinks":[],"summaries":[],"title":"卓宏謀《南洋群岛游记》","unimportant":[{"date":"2025-03-24 22:14:40","docid":0,"group":[{"date":"2025-03-24 22:14:40","docid":0,"id":5,"linecolor":"ffaa0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":3,"page":21,"rect":[170.24999492615476,109.4999967366458,176.24999474734085,482.2499856278305],"type":1,"uuid":"013f323936289789af2c01a0bc3981ab"}],"id":4,"imgfile":"6937a991f2ade3c252a811230c11371f.png","linecolor":"ffaa0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":3,"page":14,"rect":[448.4999866336588,112.4999966472388